title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps all the action from the NFL weekend. When's the last time the Jets, Giants, Jags, and Washington have won on the day? Ross Tucker discusses whether or not there should be any concern surrounding the Broncos. And Tim Tebow tells us which celebrity has his Heisman Trophy.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
